descriptions.description: Buy the upcoming Apple iPhone 14 that will be launched in India on October 31, 2022 (Expected) at Rs 79,900. The mobile is expected to come with an immersive 6.1 inches (15.49 cm) display that will have a resolution of 1170 x 2532 Pixels so that you can enjoy watching videos or playing games with a crystal clear view. Besides, the phone is rumored to have 4 GB, 4 GB of RAM + 64 GB of internal storage variant. With such high internal storage, you will be able to store your videos, movies, songs and other stuff without worrying about space constraints.

The camera specifications of this upcoming phone are really impressive. On the front, the mobile is expected to feature a Dual camera setup on the rear. It will have 12 MP + 12 MP cameras that will let you click some mesmerising pictures. And, on the front, the phone is touted to sport a 12 MP + SL 3D camera for clicking selfies and making video calls.
